    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini Dei saluatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Regnantibus domno
                        Desiderio et Alhelchis excellentissimis <rs key="#Emperor/king"
                        >regibus</rs>, anno pietatis regni eorum in Dei nom(ine) sexto decimo et
                        tercio decimo, primo mense iulio, indicione decima; feliciter. Scripsi ego
                            <persName key="#Notary"><name ref="Stephanus"
                            >Stephanus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> rogatus et petitus ab <persName
                            key="#Marquis/duke" ref="#people/1279">Iohanne</persName> in Dei nomine
                            <rs key="#Marquis/duke">duce</rs>, ipso presente, adstante, michique
                        dictante, quique fatetur se inite bone fidei, iure optimo et legibus, sub
                        duplo, bone condicionibus, sed et rei quoque instructe meliorateque,
                        taxatione habita, distraxisse et distraxi, vendidisse et vendidit ego
                        suprascriptus Iohannes in Dei nomine dux a presenti die uobis domne
                            <persName key="#Abbesses" ref="#people/1278">Anselperge</persName> in
                        Dei nomine <rs key="#Abbesses">abbatisse</rs> vel cuncta congregationis in
                            <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName
                            key="#Casalia #Fundi #Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder #Abbesses #Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/30">Domini Saluatoris</orgName>, sito infra <rs
                            key="#Walls">muros</rs>
                        <rs key="#Cities">ciuiatis</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Walls #Cities" ref="#places/9">Brixie</placeName>, id est
                        in <rs key="#Fundi">fundoras</rs> seu <rs key="#Casalia">casalias</rs> qui
                            <rs key="#Canals">reiace trans</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Canals #Confinia" ref="#places/3623">Mucia</placeName>, qui nobis per dono et <rs
                            key="#Imperial/royal_diploma">precepto</rs> a regia potestate concessa
                        sunt, ad pertica legitima de pedes duodecim plenarios, et mensura completa
                        ad ratione facta iuges duodecentos, infra <placeName
                            key="#Casalia #Fundi #Cereals #Forests #Hay/fodder" ref="#places/94"
                            >Redduto</placeName> in <rs key="#City_territory">territorio</rs>
                        <placeName key="#City_territory" ref="#places/38">Motinense</placeName>, ubi inter adfines: ab uno
                        latere da oriente Mucia percurrente, et ab alio latere da meridie
                        monasterium <orgName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/501
                            ">Domini
                            Saluatoris</orgName> sito in <placeName key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/903"
                            >Leonis</placeName> habente, seu et a tercio latere da occidente
                        monasterium <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/47"
                            >Sanctorum Apostolorum et Sancti Siluestri</orgName> habente, atque a
                        quarto latere ab occasu <rs key="#Confinia">limite</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Confinia" ref="#places/3624">Polito</placeName>; qui nunc sunt et si quis
                        alii ad fines sunt uel ab origine fuerunt, quotquot et populus, finibus,
                        terminibus, <rs key="#Cereals">campis</rs>, <rs key="#Hay/fodder"
                            >pratis</rs>, pascuis, <rs key="#Forests">siluis</rs>, salectis,
                        sacionalibus, riuis, fontibus, aquis perhennis, uel omnibus infra se
                        habente; et infra superscripta coerentia uendimus uobis suprascriptos
                        duocentos iuges. precio autem placitum et definitum, sicut inter nos
                        conuenit, in auro solidos duocentos, et repromitto me ego suprascriptus
                        Iohannes dux, una cum meis filiis et heredibus uobis domne Anselperge
                        abbatisse uel cuncta congregatione monasterii Domini Saluatoris, sito infra
                        ciuitate Brixia, infra easdem coerentia, suprascriptos duocentos iuges ab
                        omni quemque homine defensare; et si defendere minime potuero, promitto me
                        uobis componere suprascriptos duocentos iuges, talis et alios talis, una
                        quoque inib√¨ a uobis edificauit aut melioratione fuerit in duplo. Acto in
                            <rs key="#Curtes">curte</rs> mea in <placeName ref="#places/3625"
                            key="#Curtes"><geogName key="#Curtes" ref="#estates/1148"
                                >Aquario</geogName></placeName>, <placeName key="#Curtes"
                            ref="#places/446">Monte Bellio</placeName>, territorio <placeName
                                key="#Curtes #City_territory" ref="#places/7">Bononiense</placeName>, sub die, regnum et
                        indicione suprascripta; feliciter. Iohannes in Dei nomine dux in hanc
                        cartula uendicionis a me facta, sicut superius legitur, manu mea propria
                        subscripsi. Signa manus <persName 
                            >Autelmoni</persName> germano <persName key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus"><name ref="Teudo"
                                >Theoderoni</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">castaldius</rs> testis. Stephanus
                        notarius scriptor istius cartule uendicionis post roborata a testibus,
                        tradita ea compleui et dedi.</ab>
